                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Groves argued that Bowles' experience with the task force put him in touch with North Carolinians from all walks of life and negates claims that his Washington experience isolates him from local interests.</p>
<p>"[Bowles is] a person who gets things done," Groves explained. "He's not inclined to be passive or coast through anything. He's very much intent on making something happen."</p>
